      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even sleep lately. i just lay there staring at the ceiling thinking about how everything is literally falling apart. the climate, the politics, the whole future just looks like a death sentence for everything we care about. it feels so pointless to even bother with work or school or making plans when the world is just gonna be a wasteland in a few decades anyway. like why even bother trying to build a life in a house that's already on fire?",
